<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有d橙紋青蛙之類</blockquote><br />\n植物都無<br />\n有青蛙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35424f9e7a34e98d9d45ae1cffe7ceea543dc864","tid":108071,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">有心理時鐘先</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正確答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126ceb913f954b5b652749c5ae9c0f15dfb56137","tid":108071,"uid":36559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"有人先，因為所有野都係人定出黎"},{"pid":"4d5746ee761ebe368ef8513e10d1c65846b0a966","tid":108071,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T05:59:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有人先，因為所有野都係人定出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有肥婆先有橙色褲"},{"pid":"43d3bb7e57ed1583fb113aabd8e7a51f467506c7","tid":108071,"uid":66651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:00:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03497f0b29ef1b1f4ee0351f7a7cdf17a39f5225","tid":108071,"uid":15826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:13:15.000Z","msg":"橙色係一種property <br />\n橙係一樣有橙色呢個property嘅object<br />\n而橙可以有其他property 例如係 食得嘅 甜中帶酸嘅 有核嘅 我地唔能夠因爲單單以其中一個property去判斷一個object係或者唔係橙<br />\nto a certain extent 橙可以唔一定要係橙色先係橙<br />\n結論係 橙色呢個property係獨立於橙而存在 就算冇橙呢樣野 橙色都會存在 <br />\n咁樣我地可唔可以話橙色嘅存在係先於橙？<br />\n<br />\n利申鳩up"},{"pid":"51df869fcb047d03be46c0d03efa6a106375cf33","tid":108071,"uid":66362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:16:08.000Z","msg":"個橙字係木字部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a35736bd3b761e8cbf3b69ce057a403bd8899fa","tid":108071,"uid":26701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>橙色係一種property <br />\n橙係一樣有橙色呢個property嘅object<br />\n而橙可以有其他property 例如係 食得嘅 甜中帶酸嘅 有核嘅 我地唔能夠因爲單單以其中一個property去判斷一個object係或者唔係橙<br />\nto a certain extent 橙可以唔一定要係橙色先係橙<br />\n結論係 橙色呢個property係獨立於橙而存在 就算冇橙呢樣野 橙色都會存在 <br />\n咁樣我地可唔可以話橙色嘅存在係先於橙？<br />\n<br />\n利申鳩up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又講得幾岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得有橙色先，但人類未有文字之前唔識形容佢，直到橙既出現令橙色叫橙色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939bc2a05cf18b4b2fdd55401ed5b82ee9f85016","tid":108071,"uid":500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:21:37.000Z","msg":"個post幾時變咗月經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/68462/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/68462/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b0b7b6d2d0f3eba4f20b0a31b044474cb3044989","tid":108071,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"以人類觀察黎講<br />\n有橙呢樣野先有橙色既概念<br />\n但以客觀黎計<br />\n應該有橙色先"},{"pid":"675aaede4bc217ae5915fa2683e1e1a237fb69a5","tid":108071,"uid":62955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:23:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>橙色係一種property <br />\n橙係一樣有橙色呢個property嘅object<br />\n而橙可以有其他property 例如係 食得嘅 甜中帶酸嘅 有核嘅 我地唔能夠因爲單單以其中一個property去判斷一個object係或者唔係橙<br />\nto a certain extent 橙可以唔一定要係橙色先係橙<br />\n結論係 橙色呢個property係獨立於橙而存在 就算冇橙呢樣野 橙色都會存在 <br />\n咁樣我地可唔可以話橙色嘅存在係先於橙？<br />\n<br />\n利申鳩up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗樓主既意思係點解 橙身為一個生果，但同時間又可以用黎形容一隻色呢？正如你會講紅色rather than 蘋果色咁<br />\n<br />\n咁當然，巴打你講既都岩，未熟既橙係綠色但都係叫橙。<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為係以前，自然界中得橙係橙色，所以d 人就將兩樣野連結左一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 所以應該有橙先<br />\n<br />\n利申廢up"},{"pid":"1f6c40d81fb83ac5b797848f4476e39862352da7","tid":108071,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">有心理時鐘先</span></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d4f13f6e20e0f36b079a830b16aab040f24362","tid":108071,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:48:08.000Z","msg":"以英文嚟講，橙色呢個字直到十五世紀先首次有記錄。之前一直冇一個固定嘅字去代表呢一種顏色，多數稱之為黃紅色或黃蕃紅花色。<br />\n<br />\n中文嚟講，橙色來源搵唔到。但橙其中一個發源地係華南，公元前二千五百年已開始培植。所以應該都係先有橙再有橙色。<br />\n<br />\n利申：維基講嘅"}]}